@startuml
skinparam handwritten true
title 借出图书 用例

actor "图书管理员" as Librarian
boundary "账号判断" as AccountBoundary
control "业务控制" as BusinessControl
database "数据库" as DB

frame {
    note over Librarian : **读者账号合法性验证**
    
    Librarian ->> AccountBoundary: <b>1</b>输入<b></u><font color=blue size="20">读者账号信息<u/>
    activate AccountBoundary
    
    AccountBoundary --> BusinessControl:<b>2 </b>获取<b></u><font color=black size="20"><i>账号信息<i/><u/> 
    deactivate AccountBoundary
    activate BusinessControl 
    
    BusinessControl -->>DB:<b>3</b>比对<b></u><font color=purple size="25">账号密码合法<strike>性</stroke><u/>  
    activate DB  
    
    DB -[dotted]->BusinessControl:<b>4</b>账号<b></u><font color=#FF69B4 size="28">合<color=red>法<u/>   
    deactivate DB   
    
} 

Librarian->AccountBoundary:#ref:hidden  

note right of Librarian:**借出图书**   

Librarian-->BusinessControl:<b>5</b>输人<b></u><font color=brown size="27">借出图书记息<u/>(注：原文应为“录入”、“书籍”)     
activate BusinessControl    

Business Control-->>>Database#hidden     

group #LightBlue; group end      

loop while [true] do      
        alt conditionA then             
            actionX            
         else              
             break loop         
          endif       
       repeat until false        
end     


'继续后续步骤（根据实际逻辑补充）...



@enduml